               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer against the Tongue of People, ልሳነ፡ ሰብእ፡; Net of Solomon, መርበበተ፡ ሰሎሞን፡; Asmat prayer for Self Protection, ጸሎት: በእንተ: ዓቃቤ: ርእስ:; Asmat prayer against the evil eye with the story of Jesus and the Disciples at the Sea of Tiberias, ጸሎተ፡ ንድራ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="30v" facs="003">Fols 1r–30v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3034RepCh314">Hymn to Jesus
                                                  Christ</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="31r" to="37v" facs="033">Fols 31r–37v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1878Marbab">Marbabta
                                                  Salomon</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
