                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer for Self Protection, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓቃቤ፡ ርእስ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
